text.section:
The commission shall have the following duties:
To represent the interests of bicyclists in advising the secretary on all matters pertaining to bicycles, bikeways, and their use, extent, and location;
Assist the bicycle and bikeway program in the exercise of its duties within the cabinet;
Promote the best interests of the bicycling public, within the context of the total transportation system, to governing officials and the public at large.
